data.description: This charming Brick Ranch boasts 4 bedrooms (4th bedroom is being used as a living room)  and 2 bathrooms with the added bonus of a separate apartment over the garage, complete with a (5th) bedroom and an additional bathroom. Situated on half an acre of land, this 2300 sq ft home is located in the highly sought-after Great Bridge school district.Offering ample space for comfortable living and entertaining and with an attached garage, equipped with heating and cooling, this home presents endless possibilities - whether you envision a workshop or home gym.Step outside and unwind in your fence backyard, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying some well-deserved relaxation. Flood Insurance Required.
